Activity Summary: Type of compound activity based on both the AhR agonist mode readout and the cell viability counter screen.
AhR Activity: Type of compound activity in the AhR agonist mode screen.
AhR Potency (uM): The concentration of sample yielding half-maximal activation of AhR.
Viability Activity: Type of compound activity in the cell viability counter screen.
Viability Potency (uM): The concentration of sample yielding half-maximal inhibition of cell viability.
